Aha Al-Zoubi, El-Zoufi, Zoubi, Zouabi, El- Zaabi, Zoabi ma ọ bụ Zuabi (Arabic: ) bụ ezinụlọ Levantine a ma ama nke a na-ahụ ndị otu ya n'ụwa ndị Arab, mana ha kacha lekwasị anya na Northern Jordan, Ndịda Syria, na Palestine. Ezinụlọ ahụ bụ ezinụlọ Hasanite, Hashemite nke na-achọpụta agbụrụ ya na Hanbali Sunni Saint Abdul Qadir Al Gilani.
